Enum AppPropertyType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AppPropertyType>
      • djf.settings.AppPropertyType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AppPropertyType>

    public enum AppPropertyType
extends java.lang.Enum<AppPropertyType>
    This enum provides properties that are to be loaded via XML files to be used for setting up the application.
